name: Api NSW
body:
### Welcome to API NSW.
This is where we will be listing APIs that are available, coming soon or have been requested.

### Government Templates
We’ve crafted some government templates for you to use. Go ahead and look at what's available to fast track you and your company's development work towards direct integration with government systems for checking public registers and other transactions as they become available.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with our API portal? Check out our [documentation](https://docs.api.nsw.gov.au) or [contact support](https://onegov.nsw.gov.au/contact/apisupport) and we’ll help you sort it out.
